3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - Fuzzy DLs are also used in machine learning for handling uncertainty in data. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper mentions algorithms for reasoning under fuzzy ALC, which falls under the category of data structures and algorithms.
